node.text: 😂I am surprised that they can share eyes.

The last day of April. Hoping for a better May. 🤍🤍🤍 Freya, seeing the world with different eyes.... literally! 👁👁 #resinenchanteddoll #resinenchantedbjd #marinabychkovadolls #bjd wig by @isadorasatelier Face up by @blytheboi Eyes borrowed from @ddanne1984 #enchanteddoll #dollphotography #dollphotogallery #dollportrait #hope #stayinghome #stayathome #circuitbreakersg #day22 #pedigreesindyclothes #sindywedding #resinbjd #bjdstagram #dollstagram #sindypedigreefashion
@chersg well, we did think the circuit breaker was ending May 4 initially. 😅 But Freya is a drama queen doll, she’s meant to be melancholy 😏
Looks so drama 😄😄
@liburdystar 😘 Thank you. I think it’s a universal feeling that our view of our life and what was normal, may never be quite the same again. Hope all is well at your end 💕💕
@anya_sasha Love the pattern on the table or rug in the background too 😉. A little too quiet here.  My kids are looking sad like Heidi, no swim lessons, no ballet 😭

@liburdystar Thank you! 😊 It’s my old painting sample. Have been wanting to try it as a backdrop for awhile. Soon, Swimming and ballet will be open again! 👏🏼👏🏼 For us, one more month to go. I hope they lift your lockdown sooner. 💕
Love the irony in that comment about her eyes!! ❤️
@belle.lodge 💕💕 thanks J! Yes she’s dreaming of a great May! 💕
awww dreamy Freya is here to steal hearts 😍😍💕💕😘😘😘
@alice_in_wonderland_xoxo thank you! 😘
@aeroksana thank you! She’s borrowed the spare eyes from my DDAnne doll. It’s smaller than her Resin enchanted doll eyes that was on her. The RED eyes I had on her were a bit hard to photograph. 💕
@aeroksana о, да, поэтому я тоже поменяла своей RED глазки на поменьше 😍🙌🌷
@aeroksana I think it translated that you also changed the eyes on your lovely girl! Beautiful eyes! 💕
😱😍 Freya is stunning! Love her eyes, so expressive 😍
@anya_sasha haha anytime 🥰💕
@sparklebjd_sales thanks for encouraging me to try a change!
@poshpearl April kinda flew by.. so let’s hope May will too! 🙏🏼💕
Omg I didn’t even realise the connection of 30th April and last day of the month 😭😭😭

@eiko82dolls thank you! I ordered a spare set of eyes for my DDAnne doll. Thought I would try them as Freyas gray eyes were hard to photograph with less light available. I also have a spare set of resin ED eyes that are the same colour as Cornelia’s. It works too! But I thought I will change it up for now. Will send you a DM later with a pic of the other eyes
Those eyes are stunning. Where did you find them?
@blytheboi 😅 it was stressful Freddy.. but thank you for encouraging me though it took a few years to try
Exhilarating ❤️🙏🏻💖
@ddanne1984 it’s a little bit small but I think it’s fine for this girl coz it’s European sculpt and eye opening seems smaller than the asian sculpt. So pretty on her! 💕
😂I am surprised that they can share eyes.
